    public class AbstractDotHtmlLabelProposalProvider
extends org.eclipse.xtext.ui.editor.contentassist.AbstractJavaBasedContentProposalProvider
    Represents a generated, default implementation of superclass AbstractJavaBasedContentProposalProvider. Methods are dynamically dispatched on the first parameter, i.e., you can override them with a more concrete subtype.
